# 🖼️ Django Art Gallery Project

A full-featured art gallery web application built with Django. Users can upload artworks, browse by category/style, comment, like, and manage their profiles.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

art_gallery/
├── manage.py
├── requirements.txt
├── art_gallery/ # Main project settings
│ ├── settings.py
│ ├── urls.py
│ └── wsgi.py / asgi.py
├── gallery/ # Main app
│ ├── models.py
│ ├── views.py
│ ├── forms.py
│ ├── urls.py
│ └── admin.py
├── templates/ # HTML templates
│ ├── base.html
│ ├── gallery/
│ └── registration/
├── static/ # Static files (CSS, JS, images)
├── media/ # Uploaded images

